content.query:
SELECT [ecEventGkey]
,[cheKind]
,[cheName]
,[Month]
,[Week]
,[lastEstMoveTime]
,[Year]
,[moveKind]
,[unitIdName]
,[cheID]
,[EcEventTime]
,[type]
,[subType]
,[typeDescription]
 FROM [dbo].[ecevents]
 Where Week = 46 and Year = 2024 and unitIdName = 'CGMU5140040'
 order by [EcEventTime] asc
